主要翻译
 
motivate [sb] # vtr (stimulate to act)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 动员 dòng yuán  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 鼓励 dòng yuán，gǔ lì TC Traditional Chinese 鼓勵 
 -- How can we motivate the students to work harder?
 -- 我们该怎么鼓励学生，才能让他们更勤奋？
 
motivate [sb] to do [sth] v expr (stimulate to act)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 激励某人做某事  
 -- We need to motivate our staff to generate more profits.
 
motivate [sth] # vtr (prompt, provoke)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 激起 jī qǐ TC Traditional Chinese 激起  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 激发 jī qǐ，jī fā TC Traditional Chinese 激發 
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 导致 jī qǐ，dǎo zhì TC Traditional Chinese 導致 
 -- The burglaries motivated an increased police presence.
 -- 多个劫案导致这里的警察增多。

在这些条目还发现' motivate '：
在英文解释里：
actuate - animate - drive - drive yourself to - energize - inspire - make tick - move to action - shame - stimulate
中文：
驱

